Latest trunk - r22803. This basically prevents from doing any compiler compilation in eclipse.

To reproduce:

{code}
scala -cp lib/fjbg.jar:lib/msil.jar:build/quick/classes/compiler/ scala.tools.nsc.interactive.BuildManagerTest -d /tmp/ -cp lib/fjbg.jar:lib/msil.jar:lib/jline.jar:/usr/share/ant/lib/ant.jar:build/pack/lib/scala-library.jar `find src/compiler/ -iname "*.scala"`

